Insider Activity


Individual




Chad R. Richison



Mr. Chad Richison is President & Chief Executive Officer at Paycom Payroll LLC, a Manager at Kilpatrick Partners LLC, President & Chief Executive Officer at Paycom Payroll Holdings LLC and President & Chief Executive Officer at Paycom Payroll Merger Sub LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Paycom Payroll LLC, Paycom Software, Inc. and Ernest Group, Inc. Mr. Richison also served on the board at Ruby Groupe, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Central Oklahoma.



